headline: Gartner Earnings Surpass Estimates in Q2, Revenues Increase Y/Y
summary: IT posts strong second-quarter 2025 with EPS up 18.5% and revenues rising 5.6% y/y, but trims its full-year revenue and EBITDA guidance.
